➜海口华彩华邑乘风破浪，来海口旅游赶快收藏起来
http://www.sohu.com/a/412947346_376420	30176
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200813/4510faacf9224e3f8f3a999a37dfef37.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200813/63a041cccfce4c6183e95edcac882b84.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿上比基尼和我们一起浪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乘风破浪在海口，自助海鲜吃到爽，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>华邑邀你来海口度假啦！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200813/89127acb4f0d4d6d94d62eb52a2060e6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
