<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200813/da6d2a6454b6462eae27d3b686dd1e04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>high</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏日旅行打卡胜地，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帆船下午茶，夜晚浪漫露天吧台，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美味海鲜自助餐，你能想到的，这里都有！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200813/7a8c86105ab64abdb121cc16120c86e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>炎炎夏日，旅行必来海口度假！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/63a0d6f9587c46f1a24b93bdc15e7074.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/e4e950b10dee4027b223ef6f5c9ffc3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/24b3e3fb8c9a4c5992a8fd0dcc3ba469.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200813/b372cf3945654cf882f289fcb3e47c31.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美好生活从海上开始。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/c169cd80c30d4d0caa624ed2eb72b644.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200813/dac0e076cc24435b9e758e914617060a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海南椰林风情吸引了海内外的游客前来游玩，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很多姐妹下了飞机直奔海口华彩华邑酒店，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就为吃一口美味的面条，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">筷子夹起，簌簌簌地吸上一口，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>口感劲道的面条，味道独特爽滑，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>粗细均匀的手作面是华邑的招牌，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有时候一碗面就能吃到热泪盈眶。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/526a336c3fcb46b9873150e830f57d5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一、美味的海鲜自助餐厅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜艳全日餐厅，出品的是<strong>主题风味海鲜自助晚餐</strong>，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">琳琅满目的美食让人看了垂涎欲滴，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200813/cffd78b153764246bcc121a32c1fd5a5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/6f8a31f09ca64796b3ced2df5ed1f09e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/68cc9991fc7947eda299326a273bdd74.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200813/8f5ea58bef264c9aa13652cd2e18861d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有油焖小龙虾，有五色的蛋糕，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有高级厨师精心为你布置的西点，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特别是那草莓冰淇淋，红艳艳，秀色可餐，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/ffc04d2de2c7438390ba8285f8010962.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抿上一口，唔~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清沁入肺，甜而不腻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/e594398a1e124f1fbe28fc12f1438dbb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200813/238b397a18ea4b4eaeb8470e9db58d86.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二、精品美味的下午茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1.乘风破浪的下午茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海口华彩华邑酒店有特色的<strong>帆船美食下午茶</strong>，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即乘风破浪双人下午茶，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迎着海风，登上帆船，扬帆起航。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/a67c9228206a413ab2e8c0774b4fb11b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">广阔的大海一望无际，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海浪拍打着船身，微微摇晃，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满满可口的水果拼盘，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颜色各异，搭配地甚是好看；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爽口的饮品喝上一口，心旷神怡，好不惬意。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200813/d1b824be4b8b482c8ca22d50cb07ad0d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200813/ec2711447e944887a59727e0ad3b5240.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">午后阳光正好，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">慵懒地躺在椅子上，微风拂面；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿上心爱的比基尼，站在帆布旁，尽情地凹造型，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一帧出来的都是大片，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天，你就是乘风破浪的主角！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（注：乘风破浪下午茶用餐地点—华彩天空吧）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200813/da15b63c9eea4822abc5680f141ac6bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200813/ba29fdfd66034fd99d1042a82800812c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2.大堂酒廊下午茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了在帆船上体验下午茶外，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你还可以选择在大堂酒廊里享受下午茶，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐在大厅的沙发上，轻轻抿一口鸡尾酒，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以彻底放松自己的心情，调慢节奏，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去融入到这夏日连绵里。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>精致的水果拼盘，五色各异</strong>，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>搭配着让人垂涎欲滴的茶点</strong>，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当午后的阳光洒进来，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">折射的光在桌面如跳动的精灵，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一处角落都是打卡拍照的好地方，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200813/9c8f1901f32f4ec3a301fd193f7baa06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">静谧的时光里，端一杯咖啡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或与好友洽谈，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或携本小书，低头专心致志研读，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或小憩，放开心灵，去追逐梦和诗意。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200813/cc8faf427cc344b88330b31abf3312c2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>三、摩登时尚的华彩天空吧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来到酒店11楼，音乐声先入耳，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夕阳藏在海的地平线那头，一点一点下沉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在帆船上享受海风拂面，再来到天空吧品味下午茶，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天空吧的露天大平台，最适合叹叹人生，看云卷云舒，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和朋友或情侣们一起约会，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>双人或多人一起聚餐是最适合不过了。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200813/1aeb9d189d5342cb8572cc6705a47257.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上<strong>羊排，烤肉串</strong>等，肉香袅袅升起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在烤炉架上薄薄涂上一层油，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/9d735a698b3f480293d235285fedf007.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200813/15823caf95bf4d3ca96e8d36495a9af2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/cce55173895041aab52601e6c5dfb5c6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/df6ee9bc3f144eb0bc4242adf635192d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">窜入你的鼻子里，还未开吃，就口中生津了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/5c0f62fb99bc41448e9738ebf80e6ee8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/fcf2df6bbd914269968ba66a83cc218a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200813/99d5dfbf3ac24a8495aaf1cc9756e8b0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/f9c41ae500c14639b94aa7a28c9e0fe0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时间过得飞快，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚霞把天空映的红彤彤的，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">华彩天空吧笼罩在一片红晕中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚霞笼罩之下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玻璃杯折射着迷幻的灯光，如同魅影一般，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">条纹式样的小舞台设在品酒区中央，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>来宾举杯欢祝美好时光，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>摩登风格和现代都市化气息相碰，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们的笑声和碰杯声交织在一起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落日后，时尚潮流正式开启。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/2765c73411604fc79f559a2035b99eb1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200813/0ddcec5dc280470186fb24ea61bc38c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在露天吧台向远处眺望，<strong>世纪大桥尽收眼底</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜晚，大桥如一条沉睡的巨龙卧在海上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">桥上的霓虹闪烁，夺目绚丽，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两岸的灯火辉映，现代化的气息弥漫，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与友人并肩站一起，轻轻捧杯，开怀大笑，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">繁星似乎都落到了对方的眼眸里，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四周，大家跟随着音乐来律动，氛围浪漫又高级。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200813/420cc73c3ceb41ef90289a971da624cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200813/27d3c99468c447c3a64547aaa6783ac5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200813/1fa5df0e123541c5ad10a21abd125302.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">活在当下，人生须得尽欢，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">旅行的意义不是如此吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯有美食和旅行不可辜负，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>让我们乘风破浪，满载而归！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/c783694050924bd491422a8318370da7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>海口华彩华邑酒店</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200813/f504c8a2868f4d11b471e809a68be482.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>酒店地址</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海口市美兰区碧海大道21号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>营业时间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天空吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下午茶：17:30~18:30</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">韩式烧烤：17:30~21:00</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鲜艳全日餐厅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自助晚餐：18:00~21:00</p>
